-- UBM says in talks to buy US trade show rival Advanstar
-- By Noor Zainab Hussain in Bangalore
-- Thu Sep 18, 2014 02:47AM EDT
-- None



Sept 18 (Reuters) - UBM Plc <UBM.L>, a British communications and events company, confirmed that it was in talks to acquire Advanstar, a privately held U.S. trade show organiser.

UBM, which also owns PR Newswire, said on Thursday it was involved in discussions which may, or may not, lead to a transaction. Reuters reported on Tuesday that UBM was in advanced talks to acquire Advanstar for around $900 million. [ID:nL1N0RH0ZO]